window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Varg has already completed no few tests in order to consider himself an experienced survivor in this world of zombies. But will that actually be enough? After all, fate is no slacker, the system neither, and it is quite probable that these two capricious ladies have joined forces.</p> <p>His future involves more tests in new worlds. Will he meet a new friend there? Or will he meet hoary vampires? Or maybe a mysterious lady to rescue in her hour of need. Or perhaps all this and more. Who knows?</p> <p>Well, the system knows, for sure, seducing Varg with ever newer tasks.</p>"; 
